                    <span>For me, if I wrote a book, I'd want it to have all of the production values of this book.<p>The layout gets an "A".<p>I like the chapter sections with a `binding of content' in the quotations used and the graphics employed.<p>This is a beautifully compiled book.<p>Three problems.  Content, content, content.<p>I also have books on bookbinding, the art of making your own books.  This book will move from my technical bookshelf to my "Arts in creative bookbinding" shelf.<p>This is truly a beautiful book.  What I'll learn regarding the GoLive 6 application will be minimal but what I've gained on modern layout is outstanding.<p>I'm sure the editor of this book an I are best friends.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Book with great content</div>
