                    <span>I've had this book since it was released and it really helped my learn how to use GoLive 6 as I already know how to do web pages and such.  Having used Dreamweaver for many years, the way GoLive works is completely different and this book was a good guide on figuring out how to get what I wanted done, done.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">An Excellent Book for those who want to know more about GL6</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
